  "body": "***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: Switching between main screens (Home-Wallet-Profile) on iPhoneX has a noticeable side-effect of jumping bottom panel. We need to \"bind\" this tab panel to bottom device screen on appropriate views (Home, Wallet, Profile). \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThere is no flickering of the bottom tab panel when switching between tabs on an iPhone X\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nBottom tab panel jump around when switching between tabs on an iPhone X\r\n![iphone x jump](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/37775900-d4e5c652-2dec-11e8-9dc0-79d0c2798a57.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status and log in to account\r\n- Switch between screens (Home -> Wallet -> Profile -> Wallet -> Profile) and keep an eye on main tab panel\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop (284th jenkins build), Release 0.9.15+\r\n* Operating System: iPhoneX (iOS 11.2.5)\r\n\r\n",
